X-AC-Auth-Token.name: X-AC-Auth-Token
X-AC-Auth-Token.description:
* Every request requires an access token which is passed in as a special header called X-AC-Auth-Token

Curl example to get a list of products:

```shell
curl -H 'X-AC-Auth-Token: 7ccdb91...dfd0' https://youstore.americommerce.com/api/v1/products.json
```
